parent-teacher conferences

00:00:23.857 --> 00:00:25.316 position:50% align:center
right after summer break.

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:27.152 position:50% align:center
So don't forget to let
your parent or guardian

00:00:27.235 --> 00:00:29.362 position:50% align:center
